page.javamath.desc: convert math equations into mcfunction form. also includes variable support!
page.javamath.info:
- Using [<command>] would be considered as the result of the command. For example [time query gametime] would substitute into the game time in ticks.

- Math functions are not yet supported.
page.midinoteblock.desc: convert MIDI files into noteblocks packed in mcfunctions!
javamath.prop.fractional_precision.desc:
Determines the accuracy of floating numbers.
This means that variables' last N digits are treated as floating points.
